##It was the best of times. It was the worst of times.

Micro Signal RSZMDFJ

Function introduction, human is the scale of all things, human is the most beautiful scenery.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
March 17,2020.

The 24th day of the second lunar month.

Wuhan closed for fifty-five.

Day Four of the opening of Heaven's gate.

In the history of mankind, disaster, fear and war are the norm. Four decades of global peace and prosperity are rare. It is also very rare for a person to go through life without war, without economic collapse, without social unrest. We live in a very fortunate time. And we don't even realize it. Nor do we realize how unusual this kind of luck is. And how fragile it is.

Sometimes, as we go from day to day, we have the illusion that tomorrow will be the same as today and the day after that will be the same as tomorrow. The great changes of history are only written in the history books. They have nothing to do with us. Until the ice of history opened up a huge crack in front of us

As the ice of history cracks before our eyes, Absalom
